name: Cargolux 747-4R7F [LX-SCV] Close Up Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Nice to see this bird in daylight again! Here we have a 15 year old Cargolux 744 taxiing up close on Bravo and departing runway 17L on Saturday, November 5th. Coincidentally, this is the exact same 747 I caught back in September, landing on the exact same runway. ATC is included, enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
